Common.LongDescription.Common.Text: Strategically located on Loop 101 just north of Shea,Raintree Corporate Center is a Class A office complex that provides easy access and excellent visibility. Common.LongDescription.Common.Text: This office building recently had a major rehabilition completed (October 2002).  Interior common areas, and the exterior of the building were repainted, new floor and ceiling tile was installed, the windoww were retinted and the property was relandscaped, including the retiling of the fountain.  Drinkwater's Steakhouse (open for dinner only) opened on the first floor at this time, as well.  In addition, this property is located near many other area restaurants, hotels, and shopping centers.
